	
	Major new version released! (2.0.0)
	
	- Improved stability
	- Added much request 'step' feature, which allows the slider to snap in place.
	- Added touch support for iPad, iPhone and other 'touchstart' capable devices.
	- Fixed many bugs.
	- Drasticly improved stylability, and added a new -much smaller- default stylesheet.
	- Reworked the entire documentation.
	- Reduced the ammount of options, without reducing features.
	- noUiSlider examples page provides detailed examples.
	
	View documentation on:
	
	http://refreshless.com/nouislider/